&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Business Development Representative is key to growing our new territories and developing our existing territories. In this position, you will travel 2 weeks out of the month to any of our 100+ territories throughout the United States! The other 2 weeks out of the month, you will manage a small territory in your home city.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be connecting with pediatric practices across the country, educating them on the DOC Band®’s and EarWell®’s benefits, and driving referrals to our clinics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
