&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our most successful hires have come from backgrounds in Machine Shops, Plumbing, Carpentry, Construction, or other Craftsman Trades!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be working with a dynamic group of employees who are passionate about the work they do and are dedicated to the babies we treat. Our team members enjoy working in an invigorating environment, have an interest in learning in a collaborative setting, and most of all bring a positive attitude!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In addition to being part of the team that manufactures the DOC Band®, we offer an outstanding work environment: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
