&lt;li&gt;Work Monday - Friday, with no shift work, no nights, and rare weekend work. (Typical schedule is Monday - Friday 5:00AM - 1:30PM or 5:30AM - 2:00PM)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We will train you to perform the work and help make you successful in the position with a typical 4-6 week training period.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work inside (in the A/C) our new fabricating area located in Chandler. It is one of the cleanest in Arizona!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
